'''坐視要管'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20100123/00476_001.html|publisher=[[太阳报_(香港)|太阳报]]|title=佐治古尼捐逾千万兼做接线生- 太阳报|date=2010-01-23|accessdate=2020-07-23|archive-date=2010-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101222172636/http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20100123/00476_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Not On Our Watch}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/2979614|publisher=[[英文台湾日报|英文台湾日报]]|title=内战与财富 乔治克隆尼揭南苏丹敛财黑幕|date=2016-09-03|accessdate=2020-07-23|archive-date=2020-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724021441/https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/2979614|dead-url=no}}</ref>，缩写：'''NOOW'''）是一个[[总部|总部]]设在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的专注于[[国际救济|国际救济]]和[[人道主义|人道主义]]援助的[[非政府组织|非政府组织]]。该组织由[[唐·钱德尔|唐·钱德尔]]、[[乔治·克隆尼|乔治·克隆尼]]、[[麦特·戴蒙|麦特·戴蒙]]、[[布莱德·彼特|布莱德·彼特]]、[[戴维·普雷斯曼|戴维·普雷斯曼]]（David Pressman）以及[[杰里·温特劳布|杰里·温特劳布]]（Jerry Weintraub）等人在2008年共同创立，目的是让全球关注[[达尔富尔|达尔富尔]]及其他地区的[[侵犯|侵犯]][[人权|人权]]的行为，同时提供资源协助结束世界各地的大规模[[暴行|暴行]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://foundationcenter.org/pnd/news/story.jhtml?id=238200041 |title=Oxfam America Receives $500,000 From Not On Our Watch |publisher=FoundationCenter.org |date= |accessdate=2020-07-23 |archive-date=2013-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130303210353/http://foundationcenter.org/pnd/news/story.jhtml?id=238200041 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://notonourwatchproject.org/who_we_are |title=Not On Our Watch |publisher=Notonourwatchproject.org |date= |accessdate=2020-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917221559/http://notonourwatchproject.org/who_we_are |archive-date=2017-09-17 |url-status= |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

坐视要管的运营基础源于钱德尔和[[人权活动家|人权活动家]][[约翰·普伦德加斯特|约翰·普伦德加斯特]]（John Prendergast）共同撰写的《[[坐视要管_(书籍)|坐视要管：终止达尔富尔及其他地区群体灭绝的使命]]》一书<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/14/6/6/n4172211.htm|publisher=[[大纪元时报|大纪元时报]]|title=挺身而出倡导人权的九位明星|date=2014-06-06|accessdate=2020-07-23|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723091400/https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/14/6/6/n4172211.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，普伦德加斯特是董事会成员并担任战略顾问<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.looktothestars.org/charity/540-not-on-our-watch |title=Not On Our Watch: Celebrity Supporters |publisher=Looktothestars.org |date= |accessdate=2020-07-23 |archive-date=2012-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614082557/http://www.looktothestars.org/charity/540-not-on-our-watch |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Not On Our Watch Project|date=March 17, 2011|url=http://notonourwatchproject.org/|access-date=June 21, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070512213019/http://www.notonourwatchproject.org/|archive-date=2007-05-12|url-status=|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。该组织争取艺术家、活动家和文化领袖的支持，以提高公众对其活动的[[关注度|关注度]]，同时与克隆尼、普伦德加斯特联合创办<ref>{{cite web |url=http://satsentinel.org/our-story/partner-organizations |title=Partner Organizations | Satellite Sentinel Project |publisher=Satsentinel.org |date=2011-06-30 |accessdate=2012-06-22 |archive-date=2012-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120620195959/http://www.satsentinel.org/our-story/partner-organizations |dead-url=no }}</ref>的[[卫星哨兵|卫星哨兵]]项目直接合作<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.space.com/25964-george-clooney-satellite-sentinel-human-rights.html|title=George Clooney's Satellite Sentinel Project for Human Rights Enters New Phase|work=[[Space.com|Space.com]]|access-date=2020-07-23|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723103545/https://www.space.com/25964-george-clooney-satellite-sentinel-human-rights.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

